Even if it produces electricity at an irregular rate (i.e. the power output is irregular), it'll still produce an amount of energy over a given time period. And in terms of the effect you want (i.e. at periodic milestones the SCP makes an encouraging noise) it makes much more sense for that to be after it produced a set amount of energy, rather than just because it was briefly at a particular threshold rate  of energy production, which only occurs randomly anyway.







